notes: Iraq-KRI (Duhok) profiling of urban/out-of-camp IDPs, Syrian refugees, and host populations with data collected during June 2016 (report published September 2016). The exercise included a household survey administered to a sample of 1,205 households (394 IDP, 402 refugee and 409 host households). Data can also be explored through the DART: http://www.dart.jips.org/.
